OL,3,CTwo men convicted of terror attack
OL,4,Cplot to kill Jewish people in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FTwo men have been found guilty of
OL,8,Fplotting to carry out an Islamic State-
OL,9,Finspired terror attack against Jewish
OL,10,Fpeople in which police say they
OL,11,Fplanned to "bring slaughter to the
OL,12,Finnocent."
OL,14,FWalid Saadaoui, 38, and Amar Hussein,
OL,15,F52, wanted to kill as many Jewish
OL,16,Fpeople as they could in a gun attack
OL,17,Fin Manchester.
