OL,4,Cplot to kill Jewish people in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FTheir plan was to target a community
OL,8,Fgathering before moving on to a
OL,9,FBritish military base for a "last
OL,10,Fstand" where they sought a gunfight
OL,11,F"to the death."
OL,13,FThe pair were caught because a third
OL,14,Fman - known as 'Farouk' - who they
OL,15,Fthought was planning attacks alongside
OL,16,Fthem, was actually an undercover
OL,17,Foperative passing information to
OL,18,Fcounter-terrorism officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
