OL,4,Cplot to kill Jewish people in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FArmed police ambushed and arrested
OL,8,FWalid, in May 2024, at what he thought
OL,9,Fwas a meeting with a weapons dealer in
OL,10,Fa hotel car park.
OL,12,FFollowing a 10-week trial, it took a
OL,13,Fjury at Preston Crown Court just two
OL,14,Fdays to find the men guilty.
OL,16,FWalid's brother, Bilel Saadaoui, 36,
OL,17,Fwas also convicted. He was not
OL,18,Fplanning to take part in the terrorist
OL,19,Fattacks but knew what his brother was
OL,20,Fdoing and failed to report it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
