OL,7,FSir Stephen Watson, Greater
OL,8,FManchester's Chief Constable,
OL,9,Fdescribed the foiled plot, and those
OL,10,Fbehind it, in the starkest of terms.
OL,12,FHe told ITV News: "Today we are
OL,13,Freminded of the harm, real hatred
OL,14,Fseeks to cause.
OL,16,F"The scale of the offenders' hatred
OL,17,Ftoward our Jewish community knew no
OL,18,Fbounds.
OL,20,F"They sought to bring slaughter to the
OL,21,Finnocent."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
