OL,7,FRingleader Walid Saadaoui, of Abram in
OL,8,FWigan, saw the mastermind of the 2015
OL,9,FParis terror attacks as his warped
OL,10,Fhero, and planned to carry out his own
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FHe had access to "fierce" weapons
OL,14,Fincluding assault rifles which were
OL,15,Fcapable of firing several hundred
OL,16,Frounds of ammunition per minute. The
OL,17,Fsame type of firearms were used in the
OL,18,FParis attacks when 130 people were
OL,19,Fkilled and hundreds more were injured.
