OL,7,FWhen Walid was arrested, he had a
OL,8,Fcache of weapons in his car boot.
OL,9,FOfficers found two assault rifles, a
OL,10,Fsemi-automatic pistol and almost 200
OL,11,Frounds of ammunition.
OL,13,FProsecutor Harpreet Sandhu KC told the
OL,14,Fmen's trial the weapons had been
OL,15,Fdelivered to Walid after being
OL,16,Fsmuggled into the country, and that he
OL,17,Fhad arranged for the arrival of a
OL,18,Ffurther two assault rifles, another
OL,19,Fpistol and at least 700 more rounds of
OL,20,Fammunition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
