OL,7,FBilel Saadaoui, of Hindley in Wigan,
OL,8,Fhad introduced Walid to Hussein - of
OL,9,Fno fixed address - after meeting him
OL,10,Fat a prayer group. The latter pair
OL,11,Fplanned the attack in Manchester
OL,12,Fbecause of their shared hatred of
OL,13,FJewish people.
OL,15,FThere was a reconnaissance trip around
OL,16,FJewish areas in Cheetham Hill,
OL,17,FPrestwich, and Higher Broughton, which
OL,18,Fthey picked due to the concentration
OL,19,Fof synagogues, Jewish care homes,
OL,20,Fnurseries and schools.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
