OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FThe IS supporters discussed poisoning
OL,8,Fchildren before deciding on a gun and
OL,9,Fknife attack and "wept with joy" at
OL,10,Fthe thought of killing innocent people.
OL,12,FBut none of them were aware they were
OL,13,Fbeing watched.
OL,15,FUnder intensive surveillance, the
OL,16,FSaadaoui brothers were seen at Heaton
OL,17,FPark, in Manchester, where they prayed
OL,18,Ftogether.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
