OL,7,FWalid, Hussein and the undercover
OL,8,Foperative were also followed to Dover
OL,9,Fon a reconnaissance trip which looked
OL,10,Finto how to smuggle guns.
OL,12,FIn intercepted messages there were
OL,13,Fpromises of no mercy for the young and
OL,14,Fold, and a plan to die in a shootout
OL,15,Ffor martyrdom. Hussein said his boss
OL,16,Fwas Jewish and he would slaughter him
OL,17,F"like a sheep."
