OL,7,FMark Gardner, Chief Executive of
OL,8,FJewish security organisation The
OL,9,FCommunity Security Trust, told ITV
OL,10,FNews about what he believed had been
OL,11,Fprevented in this case.
OL,13,FHe said: "It may well have been the
OL,14,Fworst terrorist attack in British
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,F"To hear that, I think, will make
OL,18,Fpeople very, very fearful.
OL,20,F"One day, they kill Jews. Another day,
OL,21,Fthey kill other people.
