OL,7,F"We are all in this together."
OL,9,FThe Crown Prosecution Service have
OL,10,Fpaid tribute to 'Farouk' for foiling
OL,11,Fthe plot and saving lives.,
OL,13,FThe service's Head of Counter
OL,14,FTerrorism, Frank Ferguson said: "By
OL,15,Finfiltrating the gang, Farouk, saved
OL,16,Flives without question and made sure
OL,17,Fthat the plot was foiled and that the
OL,18,Fperpetrators were brought to justice.
OL,20,F"He goes with our great gratitude and
